Idols Unathi and husband Thomas's marriage falling apart&nbsp; The bubbly singer and South Africa's popular &nbsp;music show judge Unathi is going through a rough time. She and her Radio personality husband Thomas are apparently failing the vows they made to each other. Khanyi Mbau confirmed the news saying that the two are definitely having a marriage that's falling apart in their door step. Khanyi also added that she wishes the two will find their way back to each other again for their children's sake. Both Unathi and Thomas couldn't be reached for comments.